{"tid":2273286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞文革鼓勵互相監視 港國安處啟用「舉報熱線」","createTime":"2020-11-05T15:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T15:53:14.000Z","uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"be1e801e9c441caf9a631b1a48bc1937952f36de","tid":2273286,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:22:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">港國安法︱搞文革鼓勵互相監視 港國安處啟用「舉報熱線」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/NLhB0T1LKRvcyL6yRhPF9off3K8=/760x760/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JUVKCZYL4NERRBU6M6J2JKEP7I.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNLhB0T1LKRvcyL6yRhPF9off3K8%3D%2F760x760%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJUVKCZYL4NERRBU6M6J2JKEP7I.jpeg&h=b0854bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港國安處設熱線讓民眾揭發告密。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香港警隊國家安全處今日（5日）正式啟用「國安處舉報熱線」，鼓勵市民透過微信、手機簡訊、或者電郵，舉報涉及國家安全的事件，有如文革時代重臨，英國廣播公司形容為「鼓勵民眾監視鄰居告密」，不過，未知是否反應太熱烈，熱線啟用後隨即「塞爆」，微信帳號至下午一度不能正常運作。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港警方今日在其網站和社交平台宣佈，為了便利市民提供與國家安全相關的資料或舉報，國家安全處已於今日正式啟用「國安處舉報熱線」。<br />\n<br />\n「國安處舉報熱線」包括中國通訊應用程式「微信」、簡訊和電郵；但不像「反暴力報料熱線」有「Line」帳號，也不包括港人常用的WhatsApp。<br />\n<br />\n有市民在微信搜尋「國安處舉報熱線」，無法新增至通訊錄，並顯示「操作過於頻密，請稍後再試」。<br />\n<br />\n香港民主黨議員涂謹申曾批評，國安處舉報熱線旨在收集情報，認為會造成人與人之間的信任瓦解，無疑是「鼓勵文革式人鬥人」；不能讓不同聲音共存，結果只會令香港變得沉默；甚至導致社會解體，損害香港的經商環境。<br />\n<br />\n香港民權觀察成員王浩賢憂慮，舉報熱線會令市民互相監視，導致社會更撕裂，「造成文革式、互相舉報文化，加強寒蟬效應的效果。大家會擔心在餐廳吃飯討論時事問題是否被人錄音錄影，或者在社交媒體的發文擔心被人截圖通報警方，引起市民互不信任的情緒，會令社會變得很撕裂。」（香港《蘋果動新聞》報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201105/R6QIRSUHMZHURBSKGYLCWZI2FY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201105%2FR6QIRSUHMZHURBSKGYLCWZI2FY%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8h4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=e10f3fa9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201105%2FR6QIRSUHMZHURBSKGYLCWZI2FY%2F&h=4ab38ed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201105/R6QIRSUHMZHURBSKGYLCWZI2FY/</a>"},{"pid":"b719b5e90a6f746ccfce5cd240e03763d43fd067","tid":2273286,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"196f01bf487f575e2735d666366295b51d7783c0","tid":2273286,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0716ad4f1c35535d0e8c342179e4ea8192cea6","tid":2273286,"uid":380027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:29:31.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"70daa3632932c50fb22fa63f388970722232e669","tid":2273286,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"中國樓價指數涉嫌違反國安法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2250355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2250355</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舉報呢個，唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48ac46605d3ed5849c7056cd900f0903a21f8ae","tid":2273286,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"Key words:Twitter 印度手足 蓮蓬圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d17bd89dc9f8242f83a306fc69dc466ca920d6","tid":2273286,"uid":52511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"We chat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=